releases/0/tender/title: 17 072 Connected to Neighbourhoods and Services in Macclesfield
releases/0/tender/description: Cheshire East Council, through their Connected Communities Strategy is looking to provide additional resource to develop the approach around Connected to Neighbourhoods and Services.  The provider will develop a relationship with local residents and encourage resident led initiatives in Macclesfield, whilst working under the Delivering Differently brand. This work includes facilitating the development of Connected Community Centres in Macclesfield, neighbourhood partnerships, and supporting the development of the Macclesfield Community Network. Alongside this, the provider will work with CEC, supporting work to develop Connected Community Centres and Neighbourhood Partnerships in areas of deprivation in Macclesfield, Knutsford and Wilmslow.
